nodes.text: FN-3156 was a human who served as a stormtrooper in the First Order. After capturing the Resistance pilot Poe Dameron in Tuanul on the planet Jakku, FN-3156 along with FN-2198, HX-1072 and JY-834 performed a scan of Dameron's T-70 X-wing starfighter and reported that they found nothing of significance.
